name: Shaka Street Soap Works
description:
Shaka Street Soaps Works
These luxurious soaps are handmade on Maui in small batches using the highest quality of coconut oil, olive oil, rapeseed oil and coco butter.

Wanila (Vanila)- Organic Tahitian vanilla bean makes this lightly exfoliating in a creamy scent of warm vanilla and spices.

Ko (Sugarcane)- Lightly sweet fragrance of raw sugar with barely there coconut and a hint of vanilla. Made with organic coconut, it is mildly exfoliating with a soft, tropical aroma

Liilikoi (Passionfruit)- Creamy, nourishing lather with the fresh, clean scent of a passion fruit bouquet.

Melia (Plumeria)- Reminiscent of the deep pink Plumeria flower. Soft floral scent, a hint of coconut milk and luxurious, creamy lather.
